    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0160">
<l>neṭiyataṉ muṉṉa roṟṟumey keṭutaluṅ</l>
<l>kuṟiyataṉ muṉṉart taṉṉuru viraṭṭalu</l>
<l>maṟiyat tōṉṟiya neṟiyiya leṉpa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The final <foreign xml:lang="ta">-i</foreign> of a word which has demonstratives<note
              place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">cuṭṭu.</foreign></note></l>
<l>initially,</l>
<l>the final <foreign xml:lang="ta">-i</foreign> of an interrogative word<note
              place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">viṉāvu.</foreign></note></l>
<l>which has <foreign xml:lang="ta">e-</foreign> initially,</l>
<l>the final <foreign xml:lang="ta">-ai</foreign> of a word which has intially</l>
<l>the lengthened part of the demonstrative,<note
              place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">cuṭṭucciṉai.</foreign></note></l>
<l>and the final <foreign xml:lang="ta">-ai</foreign> of an interrogative</l>
<l>having <foreign xml:lang="ta">yā-</foreign> initially,</l>
<l>have, in positions stated [above],</l>
<l>the [obligatory] insertion of a plosive,</l>
<l>or the optional insertion [of a plosive] ;<note
              place="foot">i.e. demonstratives <foreign xml:lang="ta">a-, i-, u- +</foreign> final <foreign
                xml:lang="ta">-i,</foreign> e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">atōḷi</foreign> ' that place
          ' (<foreign xml:lang="ta">Nacciṉārk.</foreign>), <foreign xml:lang="ta">ivvaḻi</foreign> ' this way ' ; interrog. <foreign xml:lang="ta">e- +</foreign> final <foreign xml:lang="ta">-i,</foreign>
          e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">etoḷi, evvaḻi ;</foreign> long demonstrative + final <foreign
                xml:lang="ta">-ai,</foreign> e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">āṇṭa</foreign> ' there ', <foreign
                xml:lang="ta">iṅkavai</foreign> ' here ' ; interrog. <foreign xml:lang="ta">yā- +</foreign> final <foreign xml:lang="ta">-ai,</foreign> e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">yāṇṭai</foreign> ' where '.</note></l>
<l>thus it is said.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
